[Anton] You failed.

912
01:02:42,425 --> 01:02:43,468
You failed.

913
01:02:47,055 --> 01:02:48,431
So what does that mean?

914
01:02:49,975 --> 01:02:51,685
What does that mean, Charlotte?

915
01:02:52,852 --> 01:02:55,855
When you fail
at the things that we teach you?

916
01:02:57,524 --> 01:02:59,025
I cannot get close to God.

917
01:02:59,109 --> 01:03:01,027
No, you cannot.

918
01:03:01,486 --> 01:03:03,488
