919
01:03:03,989 --> 01:03:06,408
Squandered by your lack of ambition.

920
01:03:07,450 --> 01:03:08,743
So what happens now?

921
01:03:09,369 --> 01:03:11,288
-Now?
-Yes, what happens now?

922
01:03:11,371 --> 01:03:14,165
What happened to me,
what happened to Theis and Geoffrey?

923
01:03:14,249 --> 01:03:18,128
And every one of the chosen who failed?

924
01:03:22,882 --> 01:03:24,217
We pay the price.

925
01:03:32,475 --> 01:03:33,852
You pay the price.

926
01:03:35,520 --> 01:03:37,147
[muffled screaming]

927
01:03:38,606 --> 01:03:39,941
[sobbing]

928
01:03:42,110 --> 01:03:43,653
[grunting]

