937
01:04:58,812 --> 01:04:59,979
Please.

938
01:05:00,063 --> 01:05:03,650
Well, here is where you must play.
Where you've always played.

939
01:05:04,567 --> 01:05:06,069
Theis, Geoffrey.

940
01:05:06,152 --> 01:05:06,986
No.

941
01:05:14,744 --> 01:05:16,371
And, of course, Paloma.

942
01:05:19,457 --> 01:05:20,291
Please.

943
01:05:20,708 --> 01:05:23,211
Paloma, you can stop this.

944
01:05:23,962 --> 01:05:24,963
Please.

945
01:05:25,547 --> 01:05:27,340
We do what we need to do, Charlotte.

946
01:05:28,508 --> 01:05:30,009
