947
01:05:32,846 --> 01:05:36,015
Paloma's always adored
when you played perfectly. Well..

948
01:05:36,433 --> 01:05:37,475
we all did.

949
01:05:38,101 --> 01:05:40,019
That was always the goal.

950
01:05:40,103 --> 01:05:41,104
Right, Charlotte?

951
01:05:42,355 --> 01:05:43,481
The Perfection.

952
01:05:44,524 --> 01:05:47,652
This doesn't have to be like this, Anton.

953
01:05:51,698 --> 01:05:53,450
You really hate me, don't you?

954
01:05:54,909 --> 01:05:55,827
You...

955
