961
01:06:11,926 --> 01:06:14,637
You were students who achieved greatness.

962
01:06:15,430 --> 01:06:17,348
Just as my grandfather envisioned.

963
01:06:17,432 --> 01:06:19,684
Just like my father taught me.

964
01:06:20,518 --> 01:06:23,354
Everybody should be so lucky.

965
01:06:24,814 --> 01:06:25,690
Lizzie.

966
01:06:26,816 --> 01:06:28,151
Were you abused?

967
01:06:29,110 --> 01:06:31,696
Is that what you would call it,
what we did for you?

968
01:06:38,495 --> 01:06:39,954
To play that music,

969
01:06:41,372 --> 01:06:43,291
to achieve The Perfection...

970
01:06:48,087 --> 01:06:49,380
it was a gift.

971
01:06:55,220 --> 01:06:56,387
You see, Charlotte?

972
01:06:57,555 --> 01:06:59,599
You cut off her hand for nothing.

973
01:07:01,226 --> 01:07:02,435
Lizzie, if you would.

974
01:07:07,232 --> 01:07:08,399
Well, you must remember our...

975
01:07:09,192 --> 01:07:12,278
little rituals. The drinks, the formality.

976
01:07:14,030 --> 01:07:15,156
Consequences.

977
01:07:17,492 --> 01:07:19,160
Oh, but you were just a child then.

978
01:07:20,620 --> 01:07:22,622
