989
01:07:57,073 --> 01:07:58,908
Paloma, if you would.

990
01:08:03,788 --> 01:08:05,873
We're ready for you, sweetheart. Come.

991
01:08:06,499 --> 01:08:07,417
[Anton] Ah.

992
01:08:08,126 --> 01:08:12,714
Zhang Li, you are a very lucky girl.

993
01:08:13,131 --> 01:08:14,841
Come, come, come. Sit.

994
01:08:14,924 --> 01:08:18,678
To be able to witness
this private concert,

995
01:08:18,761 --> 01:08:20,847
