She just got here.

1002
01:08:42,327 --> 01:08:43,286
She's a child.

1003
01:08:43,995 --> 01:08:45,413
-[Anton sighs]
-Do it to me.

1004
01:08:47,749 --> 01:08:51,544
If you have to do it, do it to me, please.
Don't do it to her.

1005
01:08:52,045 --> 01:08:53,504
Anton, please, I'm begging you.

1006
01:08:53,588 --> 01:08:54,631
Stop!

1007
01:08:57,383 --> 01:08:58,635
Do it to me.

1008
01:09:00,261 --> 01:09:01,512
Play for us, Charlotte.

1009
01:09:02,472 --> 01:09:04,223
