1010
01:09:05,433 --> 01:09:06,559
Now do it.

1011
01:09:10,772 --> 01:09:12,357
Play The Perfection.

1012
01:09:18,571 --> 01:09:19,489
Play.

1013
01:09:31,501 --> 01:09:32,794
