1027
01:12:39,814 --> 01:12:42,400
I'm not some random pervert.

1028
01:12:44,652 --> 01:12:45,987
Just having a little fun.

1029
01:12:48,698 --> 01:12:50,074
You motherfucker.

1030
01:12:56,497 --> 01:12:57,999
Theis, Geoffrey.

1031
01:12:59,250 --> 01:13:01,294
Come get me when she stops biting.

1032
01:13:11,971 --> 01:13:14,473
[breathes deeply]

