1035
01:13:25,651 --> 01:13:26,944
[screams]

1036
01:13:27,445 --> 01:13:29,322
Oh, no, no.

1037
01:13:29,405 --> 01:13:31,782
Please help me!

1038
01:13:31,866 --> 01:13:33,326
[cries]

1039
01:13:34,368 --> 01:13:35,328
No!

1040
01:13:35,411 --> 01:13:36,287
Wait!

1041
01:13:36,370 --> 01:13:37,496
[sobs] No.

1042
01:13:37,580 --> 01:13:38,706
I want her first.

1043
01:13:40,207 --> 01:13:41,500
It's the least I deserve.

1044
01:13:42,126 --> 01:13:44,128
